VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bgetExternalStorageDirectory\s*\(|\bgetExternalFilesDir\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:password|token|secret|key|credential|auth|private
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects sensitive file operations targeting external storage on Android.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for External Storage Used for Sensitive File Operations.
